menu "Transmitter blink configuration"

    config BLINK_GPIO
        int "Blink LED GPIO number"
        range 0 30
        default 8
        help
            GPIO number (IOxx) driving the blink LED.

            Default GPIO8 is the onboard LED on the Espressif ESP32-C3-DevKitM/C
            reference boards. Set this to match the board you are bringing up.

    config BLINK_PERIOD_MS
        int "Blink period (ms)"
        range 100 10000
        default 1000
        help
            Full on+off period of the blink, in milliseconds.

endmenu
